    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Tempaux - A four-directional rhythm game.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137040/extras/e172486cd284924e7001ad0dc7dd30be.poster.avif?t=1745183426\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137040/extras/e172486cd284924e7001ad0dc7dd30be.webm?t=1745183426\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137040/extras/e172486cd284924e7001ad0dc7dd30be.mp4?t=1745183426\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to Tempaux. Inspired by classic, highly-replayable arcade rhythm games and their unique presentations, Tempaux seeks to provide unique, yet simplistic gameplay. Your primary objective is to venture into the depths of space and harvest the rare element known as rhythmithril. Drawing in the substance with your ship's advanced speakers, you must blast incoming asteroids with your laser beam as they hit the sweet spot. Engage in customizable gameplay attuned to accommodate both casual and competitive players, and experience a user interface inspired by the look and feel of operating systems from the past.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Key Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Precise quad-directional gameplay</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customizable user interface</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A level editor with extensive tools to allow detailed filters, shaders, and backgrounds</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul>",
